  Implement this plan?

› 1. Approve Option A (a)                  Refactor incrementally
  2. Approve Option A (fresh context)  Fresh thread. Refactor incrementally
  3. Approve Option B (b)                  Rewrite in one go
  4. Approve Option B (fresh context)  Fresh thread. Rewrite in one go
  5. Revise plan                       Provide feedback and continue planning.
  6. Reject plan                       Exit Plan mode without implementing.
  7. Continue planning                 Keep Plan mode and continue the
                                       conversation.

  Press enter to confirm or esc to go back
